c: 3
v: 14
t: "Kuda zvido zvemoyo kwakashongedzerwa vanhu, kuda vakadzi, vana, goridhe zhinji uye sirivha, mabhiza akanaka anemuchiso, nezvipfuyo uye neminda yakarimwa mune zvakanaka. Aya ndiwo mafaro ehupenyu hwepasi rino; asi Allah kwavari kune kudzokera kwakanaka (Paradhiso ine nzizi dzinoerera)"